#: paragraph:2,sentence:1
msgctxt ""
"Bill was an old-fashioned, almost Victorian transplant into this century. He"
" had very formal, perfect manners and protocol. I saw him in a lot of "
"different environments and he never lost that really charming and debonair "
"quality. In many ways he was a real chameleon. I think he was many things to"
" many people.[1]"
msgid ""
"Bill was an old-fashioned, almost Victorian transplant into this century."
msgstr ""

