#: paragraph:17,sentence:1
msgctxt ""
"Bill’s inner life can best be explored in three ways: through quotes and "
"illustrations from members of his extended ACIM family who knew him well; "
"through his own words; and through revealing comments made by the Author of "
"A Course In Miracles. My task is to facilitate joining these “voices” to "
"reveal the most comprehensive picture possible of Bill’s inner life. The "
"reason for providing an inside view is that his inner life and ours are so "
"alike. Even though the externals of our lives may look entirely different, "
"the internal process of release is the same for everyone."
